{"article_id":"lIlOwDVxPAxRFihO","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The U.S. and China were forging ahead Monday with plans for a new round of trade talks ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"as the Trump administration ' s top negotiator renewed the president ' s threat","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to raise tariffs across-the-board on Chinese imports","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"and voiced anger","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that Beijing was trying to back out of a key commitment .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"The tensions staggered world financial markets , especially in China ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"where stocks fell more than 5 % in a single day .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"The U.S. markets fared much better","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"but were also down Monday .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"U.S. Trade Representative Robert E. Lighthizer said late Monday","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"that the next round of talks with the Chinese will take place in Washington on Thursday and Friday .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"the administration plans to increase duties on Chinese imports on the \" first minute \" of Friday , at 12:01 a.m. ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"asserting","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"that China is \" reneging \" on earlier negotiations .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"\" Over the course of the last week or so , we ' ve seen an erosion in commitments by China ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"I would say","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"retreating from commitments","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"that have already been made , in our judgment , \"","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"Mr. Lighthizer told reporters .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Significant issues remain unresolved ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"including whether tariffs will remain in place ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Treasury Secretary Steven T. Mnuchin said","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"it became clear last weekend that China was moving \" substantially backward \" on some of the language on several issues","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"that Beijing previously had agreed to ,","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"and that the development could dramatically change the deal .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"the U.S. won ' t renegotiate commitments","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"that were already made .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"Mr. Mnuchin told reporters","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"that about 90 % of the comprehensive trade deal ,","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"which is more than a year in the making ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"had been finalized .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"A spokesman for China ' s Foreign Ministry said","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"a team of Chinese trade negotiators was still planning a trip to Washington .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"But spokesman Geng Shuang declined to say","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"whether top negotiator Liu He , China ' s vice premier , would participate .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"\" The urgent task right now is for the United States to work with China","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"and move in the same direction","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"so that we can reach a mutually beneficial and win-win agreement","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"based on mutual respect , \"","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"Mr. Geng said","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"told reporters in Beijing .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"Global financial markets fell sharply Monday","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"after President Trump vowed to raise tariffs from 10 % to 25 % on $ 200 billion worth of Chinese imports by the end of the week .","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"He also warned","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"that the U.S. would soon impose a 25 % tax on everything else","depth":15},{"id":48,"text":"China sells to the U.S.","depth":15},{"id":49,"text":"that hasn ' t been subject to tariffs .","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"\" The United States has been losing , for many years , 600 to 800 Billion Dollars a year on Trade , \"","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"Mr. Trump tweeted Monday .","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"\" With China we lose 500 Billion Dollars .","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"Sorry ,","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"we ' re not going to be doing that anymore ! \"","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"It marked a sharp change in tone for the president ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"who had been saying publicly in recent weeks","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"that he intended to host Chinese President Xi Jinping at the White House soon ,","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"suggesting","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"a final agreement was near .","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"Sources familiar with the talks said","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Mr. Trump issued the threat","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"after learning from Mr. Lighthizer","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"that China was trying to back out of a commitment","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"to change Chinese law","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"to reflect the terms of the anticipated trade deal .","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"The dispute has major implications for provisions of the deal","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"aimed at ending China ' s practice","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"of forcing U.S. companies","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"doing business there","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"to reveal proprietary technologies and other intellectual property ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Bloomberg reported .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Previously , Mr. Trump had postponed deadlines for a trade agreement in an effort","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"to buy more time for negotiations .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"But on Sunday , he complained on Twitter","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"that a deal with Beijing was coming \" too slowly ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"as they attempt to renegotiate .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"No ! \"","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"China ' s financial markets dropped sharply Monday","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"following Mr. Trump ' s tariff warning ,","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"leading Asian markets down .","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"The Shanghai Composite Index fell 5.6 %","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"and the Shenzhen stock exchange dropped 7.4 %","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"- their biggest single-day losses since 2016 .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"U.S. stock markets fell sharply , 450 points at the opening bell Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"but pared most of their losses throughout the day .","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"The Dow Jones Industrial Average closed down 66.47 points , or 0.25 % ,","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"to finish at 26,438.48 .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"The tech-heavy Nasdaq closed down 0.50 % ,","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"and the S & P 500 ended the day down 0.45 % .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"During a Rose Garden ceremony at mid-day","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"honoring the Army military academy ' s football team ,","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"the country is \" setting records","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"- over 100 days of stock market wins . \"","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"\" And our unemployment numbers are the best in 51 years , \"","depth":4},{"id":96,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":4},{"id":97,"text":"- This article is based in part on wire-service reports .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":195,"left":194,"right":97,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":187,"right":193,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":175,"right":186,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":175,"left":106,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":102,"right":105,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":0,"right":101,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":99,"right":100,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":99,"left":1,"right":2,"rel